text: Veit Kührt (born 3 December 1940) is a German ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the United Team of Germany Category:Ski jumpers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:People from Zella-Mehlis
